ISLAMABAD, Jun 12 (APP): The Strategic Plans Division (SPD) has got an allocation of Rs 987.084 million under the Public Sector Development Programme (PSDP) 2024-25
According to the budget document released on Wednesday, the allocation of Rs 987.084 was made for the new scheme of research and development project of Center of Additive Manufacturing for Aerospace and Biomedical Industry, Islamabad.
